{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/steam_description_title1.png?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/simple_5.gif?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>A Simple Ball Game</strong>, you will navigate your way across narrow pathways and moving obstacles, all designed to tick you off. I mean ... add some excitement to your life. With 70 unique stages, endless shortcuts to discover, and a robust set of physics, it\u2019s anything but a simple ball game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Good luck! :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/steam_description_title2.png?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/Impossible22_GIF.gif?t=1738241978\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game that proves even the simplest concept can pose an impossible challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">70 difficult stages designed to push your 3D platforming skills to the limit. From narrow pathways to sprawling puzzle-box contraptions, no two stages  feel the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 30 unlockable customizations for your ball. Some are gained by discovering hidden conditions, others by simply playing the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With practice, learn the ins and outs of the physics system, enough to maneuver the ball like a master. With so many shortcuts to discover, there\u2019s plenty of room to flex your creativity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Modern graphics and a smooth frame rate, finely tuned to make our spherical friend look exceptionally handsome.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may start to feel ... a certain way about gravity.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/simple_3.gif?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A controller is HIGHLY RECOMMENDED. And get ready for some precision flicking!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738241978","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/page.bg.jpg?t=1738241978","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/801d411d31a770a33d570233dff4271bb714d038/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738241978","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/801d411d31a770a33d570233dff4271bb714d038/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738241978","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/steam_description_title1.png?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/simple_5.gif?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>A Simple Ball Game</strong>, you will navigate your way across narrow pathways and moving obstacles, all designed to tick you off. I mean ... add some excitement to your life. With 70 unique stages, endless shortcuts to discover, and a robust set of physics, it\u2019s anything but a simple ball game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Good luck! :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/steam_description_title2.png?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/Impossible22_GIF.gif?t=1738241978\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game that proves even the simplest concept can pose an impossible challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">70 difficult stages designed to push your 3D platforming skills to the limit. From narrow pathways to sprawling puzzle-box contraptions, no two stages  feel the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 30 unlockable customizations for your ball. Some are gained by discovering hidden conditions, others by simply playing the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With practice, learn the ins and outs of the physics system, enough to maneuver the ball like a master. With so many shortcuts to discover, there\u2019s plenty of room to flex your creativity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Modern graphics and a smooth frame rate, finely tuned to make our spherical friend look exceptionally handsome.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may start to feel ... a certain way about gravity.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281330/extras/simple_3.gif?t=1738241978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A controller is HIGHLY RECOMMENDED. And get ready for some precision flicking!</p>","developers":["Pajama Town"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"}